Here's the result of the workbench job we're evaluating.

## Initial Prompt

```
<%= @job.prompt %>
```

## Job Activities

This is the work done durin the workbench job, you can use this to evaluate the thought process and the quality of the evidence gathered.

<%= for activity <- @job.activities do %>
<%= Console.AI.Workbench.Eval.activity_prompt(activity: activity) %>
<% end %>

## Conclusion

This is the final conclusion drawn by the workbench job.

```
<%= @job.result.conclusion %>
```

<%= if is_binary(@job.result.topology) && byte_size(@job.result.topology) > 0 do %>
## Topology

A mermaid diagram of the system graph at the time of the analysis.

```mermaid
<%= @job.result.topology %>
```
<% end %>


Please use this all to grade the work fairly and descriptively.
